Rating: 3
So, after reading all 73 reviews, this is what you should do: use 4T minced garlic instead of 2T, 1/4 cup water instead of 1/2 cup, 1/3 cup lemon juice instead of 1/4 cup. Add: 1 red pepper, dried plums, apricots or golden raisins and 1/2t ground ginger and some red pepper flakes to the spices used for rubbing the chicken in step No.1. DO THIS, and you will end up with a dish to remember. Bom Apetit !

